title: Reflexive Game Magic Farm + Crack.rar
description: Magic Farm is the heartwarming and entertaining story of a young florist and her cute little dragon helper! The young girl wishes to save her beloved parents, who got lost in the jungle. But she needs money so she puts her florist skills to the test! Help her grow and sell various flowers and fruits to complete more than 25 challenging quests! You will need your green thumb, as well as your business savvy and decorating skills to reach your goal, but nothing is too difficult with a little magic on your side!
